<HEADLINE>
<P>
SANTA ANA'S CHAVEZ IN MAIN EVENT AT IRVINE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ernie Chavez of Santa Ana takes on Hedgemon Robertson in the main event tonight 
in the monthly boxing program at the Irvine Marriott. 
</P>
<P>
Chavez, a welterweight with a 10-0 record, has won his last two fights by 
knockout. Robertson of Los Angeles is 21-7-1. The first of six scheduled bouts 
starts at 7:30 p.m. Tickets go on sale today at 10 a.m. at the hotel. 
</P>
</TEXT>
