<P>
June 25, 1990, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
JIM BURBA 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 6; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
